headline: 4 Reasons to Buy Uber Stock Like There's No Tomorrow
summary: Uber Technologies (NYSE: UBER) and its industry-leading mobility platform went public in 2019 at a price per share of roughly $45.  Today, Uber's share price is has risen to about $60.  The company went from burning around $4 billion per year early in its publicly traded history to generating $6 billion in FCF over the trailing 12 months.
